B.atp=new A.cw("How current is the tournament data?","The calendar refreshes automatically every Monday from PokerNews. Pull down on the Calendar screen to force a refresh at any time.")
B.atj=new A.cw("Can I filter by country?",'Yes. Tap the country filter chips below the app bar to narrow the list to a specific country. Tap "Show past" in the top-right to also display tournaments that have already ended.')
B.atB=new A.cw("Can I register or buy in through the app?","Not directly \u2014 TableLab is a tracking and study tool, not a registration platform. Each tournament card shows a link to the full PokerNews listing where registration details are available.")
